    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201230/extras/3e8f8aebdc56c501bd56ff00e0bc7e14.avif?t=1749033228\" width=616 height=72 /></span>谢莉尔，出身贵族之家的少女，一直过着宁静的生活，直到那一天，邻国瑞达大举入侵了她的祖国布鲁亚，并杀死了大部分的居民。为了寻求获得自由的机会，在证明自己的价值后，她与其他五名被俘女性女和志愿者一起加入了敌军。这样大胆的举动会让她得偿所愿吗？还是说阶下囚的日子也许会更好过一些？只有时间才能给出答案…… </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201230/extras/97335a7d716504c51b0939cb9cb52c1c.avif?t=1749033228\" width=616 height=72 /></span>经典回合制角色扮演玩法，多个队友可自行编队，拥有多个分支路线。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201230/extras/50ef8c88359829c03139d511d12997f4.avif?t=1749033228\" width=616 height=72 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201230/extras/8faabcefc7d902d97835f779bf1cb558.avif?t=1749033228\" width=616 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201230/extras/2adf35a8e5250e96874ae14d970e16b2.avif?t=1749033228\" width=616 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201230/extras/e0e65a4e787f7fa4007d483be4ba6515.avif?t=1749033228\" width=616 height=399 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201230/extras/99034bd2ab9c3837759034f3c0c6c642.avif?t=1749033228\" width=616 height=72 /></span><strong>选择队伍成员</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >队伍成员可以随时替换，每个角色都擅长不通用类型的武器或者摸法，可以搭配自己喜好的战斗风格，并针对性处理游戏中所需要对应的障碍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>分支系统</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有两条大的分支可供选择，通向何方全看你的选择。谢莉尔和她的朋友们最终会走向何方？她们的命运就掌控在你的手中……</p>",
